    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"resting\" isn't enough. i've rested. i've taken breaks. it's not some temporary exhaustion, it's just the reality of who i am. the loop is part of the design. i feel like i'm just waiting for the next collapse, and honestly, it's getting harder to see any point in even waiting for it to happen.",
